OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrice of first class stamps
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto rise to 95p             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The price of a first class stamp will  
OL,6, rise by 10p to 95p as Royal Mail seeks 
OL,7, to cover higher delivery costs while   
OL,8, the number of letters being sent falls.
OL,10,FSecond class stamps will also increase 
OL,11,Fby 2p to 68p, with the new prices      
OL,12,Fcoming into effect on 4 April.         
OL,14,FRoyal Mail said it was having to       
OL,15,Fdeliver to a growing number of         
OL,16,Faddresses, which was adding to costs.  
OL,18,FLetter volumes have fallen by more than
OL,19,F60% since their peak in 2004-05 and by 
OL,20,Fabout 20% since the pandemic began.    
